data.description: One owner 2018 Lennar Home. Terrific 2 Story Brick Home, 4/3.5/2 Car Garage, Formal Dining Room + Game Room features Kitchen w/ 36'' Designer Cabinets, Granite Countertops, Breakfast Nook & Great Stainless Steel Appliance Pkg! Open Family Room with Corner Fireplace! Master Suite w/ Garden Tub & Separate Shower, Dual Sinks & Large Walk-In Closet! Extensive Hickory Hardwood Floors; Upgrade Tile Pattern, laid diagonally; 2''Faux Wood Blinds; Crown Moulding Pkg; Covered Patio; Gas Stub at Patio; Irrigation System; Energy Efficient 16 SEER HVAC System & MORE! So many more upgrades not listed.  This home is a Wi-Fi CERTIFIED smart home featuring integrated automation and voice control with Amazon Alexa.
